parameters: Blue-haired girl: "Amakane-sama, did you call for me...?"

Sage Amakane: "As you know, this tower was built long ago to protect
the world from a terrible calamity known as the Void."

Sage Amakane: "However, whether the calamity known as the Void will
truly occur..."

Sage Amakane: "We do not even know that much, and sometimes plagued by
skepticism, the chosen ones have managed this tower for generations."

Sage Amakane: "Maiden of Light Liese... I still can't believe it, but
it seems that the time of calamity has finally arrived."
Sage Amakane: "Liese, please look at this."

Liese: "The Spring of Time and Space looks to be blackened and
stagnant... This is a premonition of the Void mentioned in
the prophecies. If left as is, this world will..."
Sage Amakane: "Yes, not just this world."

Sage Amakane: "Our floating world \N[261] is the central hub
connecting countless other worlds. If the Void arises and engulfs this
world, the others will likewise perish."

Sage Amakane: "Indeed. As the Maiden of Light, it is your duty to
confront this disaster."
Sage Amakane: "Now, hurry and prepare yourself."
